    "IntroductionThe development and application of Artificial Intelligence (AI) have significantly advanced over the past few decades, evolving from an early concept focused on emulating human intelligence to becoming a major area of global interest.",
    "AI's reach now extends across all aspects of life, offering both disruptive capabilities and the potential to shape new ways of living.",
    "This evolution has been particularly impactful in the field of education, where the integration of AI presents both promising opportunities and the risk of being overhyped [1].Generative AI (GenAI), particularly Large Language Models (LLMs), represents a significant advancement in AI technology.",
    "These models, trained on massive datasets, possess remarkable capabilities for text generation and comprehension, closely mimicking human communication.",
    "GenAI, especially LLMs like ChatGPT, represents a significant advancement in AI technology."
